projects.name: Email Microservice
projects.description: Developed a robust full-stack email microservice using node.js, express.js and mongodb. Implemented file upload functionality for email attachments using Multer, enhancing user communication. Integrated Nodemailer to compose and send emails, ensuring reliable and secure delivery. Leveraged MongoDB for efficient data storage, enabling seamless retrieval and persistence of email data.

projects.name: Car-Rental
projects.description: Car Rental allow users to rent cars for their personal use on reasonable cost. It also includes variety of cars for different people. It is built using React and designed using Html and Css. Easy to use interface to rent a car one has to put date, time and location of the pickup.

projects.name: Sorting Algorithm Visualizer
projects.description: Sorting visualizer is a web application showcasing the inner working of sorting algorithms. It includes colored representation of different steps being executed. It also visualize time and space complexities.
